      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Option D - 1, 2, 3, 4:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Asthma, laryngitis, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"10e2dee19e1692777196673db90c23\">pulmonary</span> fibrosis, and chronic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8f02e74e821692777185a0c005c508\">cough</span> are all complications of GERD.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Incorrect Options:</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Options A, B and C: </strong>These options are incorrect.</p>",
